  "prompt": "How much is hootsuite?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, Hootsuite offered several pricing tiers depending on the features and number of users needed. Typically, their plans included:\n\n1. **Free Plan** - Limited features suitable for individual users.\n2. **Professional Plan** - Designed for small businesses, often around $19/month.\n3. **Team Plan** - Suitable for small teams, costing approximately $99/month.\n4. **Business Plan** - Targeted towards larger businesses, often around $599/month.\n5. **Enterprise Plan** - Custom pricing based on specific business needs.\n\nThese prices may vary, and Hootsuite sometimes runs promotions or offers discounts. For the most accurate and current pricing, I recommend checking Hootsuite's official website or contacting their sales team directly.",
